prompts.prompt: Generate a JSON array that represents the given workout plan. The plan consists of a warm-up, followed by 3 hours of aerobic exercise (Zone 2), three sets of 30-second anaerobic exercise with approximately 10 minutes of recovery between each set, and finally a cool-down phase. The JSON should be structured with each phase of the workout as an object, specifying the intensity and duration in seconds (where applicable).
